{"TopicId":155587,"ForumId":35,"TopicTitle":"[CKAN Plugin] CKAN Mod Hider","CreatedByName":"BlackNecro","CreatedById":7728,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-26T03:06:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"BlackNecro","CreatedById":7728,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-26T03:06:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I\u0027ve returned to KSP modding after quite some time and as it turns out \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E got more cluttered than ever.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWrote a small very \u003Cs\u003Ehacky\u003C/s\u003E kerbal plugin to declutter my mod list and thought maybe someone else got the same problem and could make use of it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUsage\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust download the dll somewhere, add it as \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E plugin and you\u0027ll be able to hide mods from all filters by right clicking them and chosing hide.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThere\u0027s also a new filter in the filter list that will list all hidden mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/BlackNecro/CKANModHider/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EDownload\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/BlackNecro/CKANModHider\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESource\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnjoy your clutter free \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E list\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-26T03:06:54Z\u0022 title=\u002201/26/2017 03:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 26, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by BlackNecro\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Poodmund","CreatedById":128643,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-26T20:56:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou may want to approach the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E guy and see whether they\u0027re interested in incorporating this into their main branch. Seems super handy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Raphaello","CreatedById":172197,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-01T22:46:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks useful to me too. Installed and working well. Thanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould you mind adding another category - \u0027Favorites\u0027? Favorites would not hide, of course, but it would allow me to keep all those good mods that I do not want to have installed atm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-02T11:32:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGot a couple of small problems:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nAfter hiding some mods, Filter on Hidden. \u00A0Works. \u00A0but then filtering on ALL\u00A0won\u0027t work, only the filtered mods show. \u00A0Other filters do seem to work\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAfter doing a Refresh, hidden mods are shown (when Filter = All)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll open issues on Github for you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I love it, will continue to follow. \u00A0Thanks and welcome back\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222941666\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155587\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485989169\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172197\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Raphaello\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Raphaello said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks useful to me too. Installed and working well. Thanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould you mind adding another category - \u0027Favorites\u0027? Favorites would not hide, of course, but it would allow me to keep all those good mods that I do not want to have installed atm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI added an enhancement request for this on Github\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Raphaello","CreatedById":172197,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-02T12:04:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222942113\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155587\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221486035161\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n30 minutes ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI added an enhancement request for this on Github\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for this \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022129964\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@linuxgurugamer\u003C/a\u003E. You\u0027ve just motivated me to create an account there \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"doggonemess","CreatedById":160106,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-15T20:07:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for this. Huge accolades and awards are sure to be in your future.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}